                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230910-322-off1723 t18230910-322-cd1724"></join>, a seal, value 30 s.; a watch key, value 15 s., and a ring, value 1 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18230910-322-victim2761" type="victimName">
