                  </persName>
            . I <rs id="t18230910-322-viclabel1725" type="occupation">keep the <placeName id="t18230910-322-crimeloc1726">Magpie and Stump, public-house, in the New-road. St. George's in the East</placeName>
                     <interp inst="t18230910-322-crimeloc1726" type="placeName" value="Magpie and Stump, public-house, in the New-road. St. George's in the East"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230910-322-crimeloc1726" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230910-322-off1723 t18230910-322-crimeloc1726"></join>
                  </rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230910-322-victim2761 t18230910-322-viclabel1725"></join>. On the 6th of September, between five and six o'clock in the afternoon, I was in my bar - the prisoner came and asked for a glass of gin - he went into the tap-room; I took it to him; he said,</p>
               <p>"This won't do for me, I want my gin in a measure;" I put it into a measure, and gave it to him, and asked him for the money - he gave me 1 1/2 d.; I said I wanted 2 d.; he said he should give me no more; I insisted on having 2 d., and said I should turn him out if he did not pay me. He was going to sit down; I took and carried him to the outside door; he immediately made a short turn, and snatched at my watch; the ring broke, and he set off with the seal, and I followed and secured him about twenty yards off. He scuffled a good deal - the seal was found just by; he had thrown it into the road while I pursued him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18230910-322-person2763">
                  JOHN 
                  CHURCHILL
               <interp inst="t18230910-322-person2763" type="surname" value="CHURCHILL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230910-322-person2763" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230910-322-person2763" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am servant to Mr. Price. I picked up the seal three minutes after he was secured; it was eight or ten yards from the door.</p>
               <p>(Seal produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18230910-322-person2764">
                  FRANCIS 
                  JACKSON
               <interp inst="t18230910-322-person2764" type="surname" value="JACKSON"></interp>
