                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. I found the prisoner struggling with Price - he said he was surgeon of a frigate.</p>
               <p>The prisoner in a written Defence, stated that he was inebriated,<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182309100115"></xptr>and in the scuffle he happened to catch hold of the watch, and the ribbon broke; but denied any felonious intention.</p>
